query:
SELECT 
  COUNT(*) as total_pedidos,
  COUNT(DISTINCT o.blingId) as pedidos_unicos,
  SUM(o.itemsCount) as total_itens_esperados,
  COUNT(s.id) as total_itens_em_sales
FROM orders o
LEFT JOIN sales s ON o.blingId = s.blingOrderId
WHERE o.orderDate >= '2025-09-01' 
  AND o.orderDate < '2025-10-01'
